Step 1 - About story

On the right you can see a map with Ukrainian companies opened since 2015. Somehow Ive decided to scrape information from the map into single table and explore it in details. In the following slides you can see what I could find out.

For presentation of my work I choose flexdashboard package that is the most suitable for data storytelling.
